gb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">打开 AI 配音工具，这里用的是 Fish Audio，之前文章里讲过它的用法流程。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">官方链接：https://fish.audio/。登录后看看有没有我们需要的声音，要是没有，就提前上传一段“悟空”在电视剧里的讲话声音，十秒钟就行。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">在 Fish Audio 点语音合成，把写好的独白文案复制进去，点生成就能得到人物独白语音。</p> \n<figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;\"> \n <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/64639/1136326c-581f-4e0e-8022-6ed1f486b802.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 8px; border-top-right-radius: 8px; border-bottom-right-radius: 8px; border-bottom-left-radius: 8px; object-fit: fill; box-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 2px 4px 8px 0px;\"> \n</figure> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">接着是把配音和画面结合起来。这一步也不难，根据文案内容，找到原电视剧对应的画面片段，用剪映拼在一起，加上<strong style=\"color: rgb(53, 148, 247); font-weight: bold; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;\">转场、去重、字幕、特效</strong>和背景音乐等，就可以直接导出了。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">剪辑部分就不多说了，有小伙伴做的时候有需求可以随时后台私信。 <img src=\"https://files.mdnice.com/user/64639/dc6252b9-b680-44af-bb3d-ee83a4afb980.png\" alt style=\"display: block; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: auto; max-width: 100%;\"></p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">账号做起来后有很多变现模式，比如橱窗带货，带和账号定位接近的图书，找些相关人物传记书籍的货品。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">还有创作者分成，这类视频流量大，不管是抖音还是视频号，参与创作者分成计划每月都能有可观收入。对想搞副业或全职的小伙伴来说都是很不错的选择。</p>",
